Try PULL UP CHALLENGE, tag your friend who can do it and challenge him. 

1st pull-up - 1 second hold

2nd pull-up - 2 seconds hold

3rd pull-up - 3 seconds hold... How far you can go? My best was 13 strict reps last with 13 seconds hold :)

But of course I had preworkout Blaster Master from @bangenergy before this challenge.

 

Check @bangenergy and inventor @bangenergy.CEO - Check out this! #BangEnergy #EnergyDrink #lifestyle
